<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />Yahweh looks from heaven;</para>

<para style="q1">he sees all the people.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />From the place where he lives,</para>

<para style="q1">he looks down on all who live on the earth.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />He who shapes the hearts of them all</para>

<para style="q1">observes all their deeds.</para>
